Find and Open - 200 pts Description Someone might have hidden the password in the trace file.Find the key to unlock¬†this file.¬†This tracefile¬†might be good to analyze.
Approach We have two files: a password-protected ZIP file and a PCAP file. Upon inspecting the PCAP file in Wireshark, a base64 string was discovered.
Decoded the base64 string and found half flag
‚îå‚îÄ‚îÄ(kali„âøiasad)-[~/CTFs/PicoCTF] ‚îî‚îÄ$ echo VGhpcyBpcyB0aGUgc2VjcmV0OiBwaWNvQ1RGe1IzNERJTkdfTE9LZF8= | base64 -d This is the secret: picoCTF{R34DING_LOKd_ I tried the half flag as a password on the zip and it worked got the flag.
